Start
Enter the values of a and b
Input the operator symbol for calculation
If the operator is '+' :
        Print Result = The value of (a+b)
Else if the operator is '-' :
        Print Result = The value of (a-b)
Else if the operator is '*' :
        Print Result = The value of (a*b)
Else if the operator is '/' :
        Print Result = The value of (a/b)
Else :
    Print 'You have entered an invalid operator'
End